d h13 y1341 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review the lesson. </div><div class="t m715 x18 h2f y15d5 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON SCRIPTURE: </div><div class="t m15de x42 h15 y14f9 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts 8: 4</div><div class="t m1d85 x1b h2f y100c ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m34ca x2f h15 y100c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25. </div><div class="t m5b0 x18 h13 y18e6 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY VERSE: </div><div class="t m190e xcf h15 ydbe ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Create in me a clean heart, 0 God; and </div><div class="t m1148 x27 h15 y123a ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">renew a right spirit within me.&quot; Ps. 51: 10. </div><div class="t m14d5 x42 h67 y1197 ff6 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Narrative </div><div class="t m988 x5d h15 ye55 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m136b x4e h15 y1151 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After the death of Stephen, what experience did </div><div class="t m8bc x27 h15 y15d8 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the church pass through? Acts 8: 1. Note 1. </div><div class="t m127 x5d h15 y150b ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m488 x4e h15 y1347 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who took a leading part in this persecution? Verse </div><div class="t m3f2 x27 h15 y1066 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3; Acts 26:9-11. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
